platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Dans ce jeu d’action en 2D, défendez les temples en pulvérisant les horreurs de l’ombre à l’aide de sorts et de faisceaux lumineux massifs.
Defend temples by blasting shadowy horrors with spells and massive light beams in this stylish 2D action game.

Everyone needs a task manager – and this Apple Design Award winner is adaptable enough for anyone. Organising items is as simple as dragging them where you want them, and the Magic Plus button makes it easy to add to-dos from anywhere in the app.
在這款風格獨特的 2D 動作遊戲中，用咒語和巨型聖光對抗陰暗的恐怖生物，保衛神殿。
